Co-organizers of #IndieWebCamp #Cambridge #2015, david.shanske.com, Ben.thatmustbe.me, and tantek.com (not pictured, host Hawke.org). Photo by @halleytucker

Really great working with these folks, especially awesome seeing Ben Roberts go from first time IndieWebCamp participant last October to lead #organizer, and David seeing a need for reliable dedicated remote participation and assembling and running a solution himself.
